Quickstrike:





Quickstrike sighed at Megatron. He gave a few quick glances at the other two 
bots in the room, Bazooka and Scorponok, then glanced back to Megatron, 
looking him in the eyes. He crossed his arms over his chest. No. Trying to 
look official, he put his long fingered hand on his hip. Better. At one 
point he thought he was trying too hard, but he went on with it.

"Well, as ah was tryin' to say, boss," he said. "Ah got an idea. Ah sent two 
bots t' go find uh stasis pod wit' uh protoform an' bring it back here 
b'fore Hell Beast's troops sees it. What ah need t' know boss, is do ya 
still have them DNA from yer old troops." He sense of wonder came across 
Quickstrike, forcing him to turn his head. He made another glance at 
Scorponok.

Weren't you dead? he said to himself.
